<ab>Dem rate zu Vorcheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Reinharts <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        Swarcz <expan>Hans<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der bey ewch in gefenknuss ligt etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> des mit fleisz und lassen ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir niht erfarn können, daz der
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns oder die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht getan hab. Doch bitten wir ewch
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> knecht meren lasset, und erfürt ir an
                        im, daz er bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> oder der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>schad<ex>en</ex></expan> gewest <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e,</expan> das
                        lieszt uns wissen, so <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir darczu tun. Denn wo
                        wir ewch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
